import React from 'react'

const SerachItem = () => {
  return (
    <form className='searchForm' onSubmit={(e) => e.preventDefault()}>
        <label htmlFor='search'>Search</label>
        <input
            id='search'
            type='text'
            role='searchbox'
            placeholder='Search Item'
        />
    </form>
  )
}

export default SerachItem
